org.apache.ignite.ml.math.primitives.vector

Interface NamedVector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Destroyable, Externalizable, MetaAttributes, Serializable, StorageOpsMetrics, Vector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DelegatingNamedVector

    public interface NamedVector
extends Vector
    A named vector interface based on Vector. In addition to base vector functionality allows to set and get elements using names as index.
